OL,6,FA former subpostmaster says he only
OL,7,Fbecame aware he was caught up in the
OL,8,FHorizon scandal when he watched the
OL,9,FITV drama 'Mr Bates vs the Post
OL,10,FOffice'.
OL,12,FAndrew Tizzard from Othery in Somerset
OL,13,Fused to run a Post Office in South
OL,14,FWales with his wife Kathy.
OL,16,FHundreds of subpostmasters were
OL,17,Fpursued for apparent financial
OL,18,Fshortfalls which were actually caused
OL,19,Fby faults in the Horizon accounting
OL,20,Fsoftware.
