OL,4,Cscandal when he saw ITV drama
OL,6,FBetween 1999 and 2015 more than 900
OL,7,Fsubpostmasters were prosecuted and 236
OL,8,Fwere sent to prison.
OL,10,FA damning report into the scandal has
OL,11,Fconcluded at least 13 people may have
OL,12,Ftaken their own lives after being
OL,13,Faccused of wrongdoing.
OL,15,FIt also concluded Post Office bosses
OL,16,Fknew the Horizon IT system had
OL,17,Fwidespread faults, but had "maintained
OL,18,Fthe fiction" it was accurate for years.
