OL,6,FOn the report Mr Tizzard added: "What
OL,7,Fwe need to see now is somebody's head
OL,8,Froll for it, because it's all very
OL,9,Fwell getting some redress for it, some
OL,10,Fcompensation thrown in there, but they
OL,11,Fmade everybody's life hell, our life
OL,12,Fwas hell."
OL,14,FPenny Williams was running the Post
OL,15,FOffice in Manaccan, on the Lizard,
OL,16,Fwhen she was accused of embezzling
OL,17,F#20,000.
