OL,3,CSub-postmaster only realised extent of
OL,4,Cscandal when he saw ITV drama
OL,6,FPenny, who not only lost her post
OL,7,Foffice, but also the pub in the
OL,8,Fvillage that she had been running
OL,9,Fsince 1997 after being declared
OL,10,Fbankrupt as a result.
OL,12,FMs Williams said: "I was suddenly
OL,13,Fpersona non grata in the village as a
OL,14,Fresult of this. It was as if you're
OL,15,Fstanding on quicksand and it just all
OL,16,Fdisappeared from under me.
OL,18,F"I tried but I just couldn't stop the
OL,19,Fbankruptcy happening and then within
OL,20,Ftwo weeks, we had to be out of the pub
OL,21,Fas well."
