OL,6,FShe finally received compensation last
OL,7,Fweek.
OL,9,FMs Williams added "You're never going
OL,10,Fto get those however many years back
OL,11,Fbut at the end of the day, just now if
OL,12,Fyou've got compensation, at least you
OL,13,Fcan move forward."
OL,15,FShe welcomes the arrival of today's
OL,16,Finquiry adding: "If it's listened to
OL,17,Fand acted upon, it will definitely be
OL,18,Fa positive thing for the future."
